title: ERA MSS BVIM modules
agents: snmp
author: Kuhn & Rueß GmbH <info@kuhn-ruess.de>
license: GPL
distribution: none
description:
 Walks all eight tp<n>-bvim sub-tables under OID .1.3.6.1.4.1.11588.1.5.111
 and creates one service per (target processor, BVIM index) pair. Reports
 bvimTemp, bvimPowerX, bvimPowerY and bvimDinStatus.

item:
 "TP<n> BVIM <index>" where <n> is the target processor (1..8) and <index>
 is the BVIM row index.

inventory:
 One service per BVIM row that returns any status cell.
